SELECT a3."IDIR", t."AlwaysManual", (
    SELECT e."StatusDate"
    FROM "EnrolmentStatus" AS e
    WHERE (t."Id" = e."EnrolleeId") AND (e."StatusCode" = 2)
    ORDER BY e."StatusDate" DESC, e."Id" DESC
    LIMIT 1), (
    SELECT e0."StatusDate"
    FROM "EnrolmentStatus" AS e0
    WHERE (t."Id" = e0."EnrolleeId") AND (e0."StatusCode" = 3)
    ORDER BY e0."StatusDate" DESC, e0."Id" DESC
    LIMIT 1), ((
    SELECT s."Confirmed"
    FROM "Submission" AS s
    WHERE t."Id" = s."EnrolleeId"
    ORDER BY s."CreatedDate" DESC
    LIMIT 1) = TRUE) AND ((
    SELECT s."Confirmed"
    FROM "Submission" AS s
    WHERE t."Id" = s."EnrolleeId"
    ORDER BY s."CreatedDate" DESC
    LIMIT 1) IS NOT NULL), (
    SELECT e1."StatusCode"
    FROM "EnrolmentStatus" AS e1
    WHERE t."Id" = e1."EnrolleeId"
    ORDER BY e1."StatusDate" DESC, e1."Id" DESC
    LIMIT 1), t."DateOfBirth", t."Id" + 1000, t."Email", (
    SELECT a."ExpiryDate"
    FROM "Agreement" AS a
    WHERE (t."Id" = a."EnrolleeId") AND (a."AcceptedDate" IS NOT NULL)
    ORDER BY a."CreatedDate" DESC
    LIMIT 1), t."FirstName", t."GivenNames", t."GPID", EXISTS (
    SELECT DISTINCT 1
    FROM "AgreementVersion" AS a0
    WHERE ((
        SELECT a1."Id"
        FROM "AgreementVersion" AS a1
        WHERE a1."AgreementType" = a0."AgreementType"
        ORDER BY a1."EffectiveDate" DESC
        LIMIT 1) = (
        SELECT a2."AgreementVersionId"
        FROM "Agreement" AS a2
        WHERE (t."Id" = a2."EnrolleeId") AND (a2."AcceptedDate" IS NOT NULL)
        ORDER BY a2."CreatedDate" DESC
        LIMIT 1)) OR (((
        SELECT a1."Id"
        FROM "AgreementVersion" AS a1
        WHERE a1."AgreementType" = a0."AgreementType"
        ORDER BY a1."EffectiveDate" DESC
        LIMIT 1) IS NULL) AND ((
        SELECT a2."AgreementVersionId"
        FROM "Agreement" AS a2
        WHERE (t."Id" = a2."EnrolleeId") AND (a2."AcceptedDate" IS NOT NULL)
        ORDER BY a2."CreatedDate" DESC
        LIMIT 1) IS NULL))), t."Id", t."LastName", COALESCE(CASE
    WHEN (e7."Id" IS NULL) THEN e8."EnrolleeId"
    ELSE e7."PaperEnrolleeId"
END, 0), EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM "Enrollee" AS e2
    WHERE (((e2."GPID" IS NOT NULL) AND (e2."GPID" LIKE 'NOBCSC%')) AND NOT (EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM "EnrolleeLinkedEnrolment" AS e3
        WHERE e3."PaperEnrolleeId" = e2."Id"))) AND (date_trunc('day', e2."DateOfBirth") = date_trunc('day', t."DateOfBirth"))), EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM "EnrolleeRemoteUser" AS e4
    WHERE t."Id" = e4."EnrolleeId"), NOT ((
    SELECT s0."Confirmed"
    FROM "Submission" AS s0
    WHERE t."Id" = s0."EnrolleeId"
    ORDER BY s0."CreatedDate" DESC
    LIMIT 1)) AND (((
    SELECT e5."StatusCode"
    FROM "EnrolmentStatus" AS e5
    WHERE t."Id" = e5."EnrolleeId"
    ORDER BY e5."StatusDate" DESC, e5."Id" DESC
    LIMIT 1 OFFSET 1) = 3) AND ((
    SELECT e5."StatusCode"
    FROM "EnrolmentStatus" AS e5
    WHERE t."Id" = e5."EnrolleeId"
    ORDER BY e5."StatusDate" DESC, e5."Id" DESC
    LIMIT 1 OFFSET 1) IS NOT NULL)), a3."Id", e7."Id", e8."Id", e9."CareSettingCode", e9."Id"
FROM (
    SELECT e6."Id", e6."AdjudicatorId", e6."AlwaysManual", e6."DateOfBirth", e6."Email", e6."FirstName", e6."GPID", e6."GivenNames", e6."LastName"
    FROM "Enrollee" AS e6
    ORDER BY e6."Id"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Admin" AS a3 ON t."AdjudicatorId" = a3."Id"
LEFT JOIN "EnrolleeLinkedEnrolment" AS e7 ON t."Id" = e7."EnrolleeId"
LEFT JOIN "EnrolleeLinkedEnrolment" AS e8 ON t."Id" = e8."PaperEnrolleeId"
LEFT JOIN "EnrolleeCareSetting" AS e9 ON t."Id" = e9."EnrolleeId"
ORDER BY t."Id", a3."Id", e7."Id", e8."Id", e9."Id"
